data.description:
BETTER THAN NEW WITH UPGRADES! PRISTINE AND WELL CARED FOR home accessible to many community conveniences. **** The Owners are including these upgrades;

-ECO Water Softening System and Drinking Water System

-New Dishwasher

- Extended Concrete Patio on back and side of home

-2 Shatter Resistant Glass Storm Doors

-ADT Cameras & Security System

-Pergola with Lights

-Washer & Dryer

-Refrigerator

-Blown Foam Insulation

-Builder's Transferrable Structural Warranty

Easy living and pride of home ownership shines brightly throughout this property.

The Living Room, Dining and Kitchen together with plenty of seating and comfort. Island and Counters have White Speckled Quartz and the counters back splash are white tiles. Spacious Pantry and Cupboards for storage. Just off of the Dining area is the Back Yard and Patio with an Amazing Pergola with Lights and a nice size yard. 

The Primary Bedroom is just off of the Living area and it is extra spacious, housing a King Size Bed with additional room for furniture. The private primary bathroom has a Double Vanity, Soaking Tub, Large Tiled Shower, Private Toilet Room and a Spacious, Extra Large Walk-In Closet.

In the front of the house are the 2 other Bedrooms which can also be used for an office and allows for privacy from the Primary Bedroom. The second Bathroom is just off of the 2nd & 3rd Bedrooms.
